title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses who is to blame for Andrew Luck's early retirement. The Athletics' Zak Keefer joins the show and shares more about Luck's story.  And current LA Dodgers manager Dave Roberts discussed the future of automated strike zones and touched on how Freddie Freeman's return to Atlanta went over in the Dodgers locker room. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
